Package com.atakmap.android.cot

Interface UIDHandler.AttributeInjector

  • Enclosing class:
    UIDHandler
    public static interface UIDHandler.AttributeInjector
    Used to inject Attributes into the UIDHandler for third party plugins. Namely the Nett-T specification. This can't this be done by simply registering a new detail handler. There are provisions in the UIDHandler to have many attribute/value pairs based on how a item is known across the enterprise. This would not be able to be done via additional custom details.
